body_html: @peterjc123 Already solved by installing mkl_fft with pip. Pip also installed icc-rt, intel-numpy, intel-openmp, mkl, mkl-fft, mkl-random at the same time, so it must be some or all of these packages missing. It works now; thanks a lot for the assistance.
